name: Ghauri Dental Centre
overview: We are a group of London based Practices dedicated to consistently high quality dental care. Our Shepherds Bush branch has been operating for over 35 years – a testament to the consistency and quality of service offered. We have been awarded the coveted award of BDA Good Practice. Our Shepherds Bush Branch was commended by BDA and was awarded BDA Practice of the year award (Joint third). The Practices benefit from state of the art technology and equipment with ambiance to match. We pride ourselves on our warm, caring and professional approach dispelling any anxiety patients may have. We also have Dentists who have a special interest in a particular field of dentistry. Consequently we are able to provide a One Stop Service including dental implants, cosmetic dentistry, orthodontics (including Invisalign), endodontics, Cerec & specialist hygienist services and sedation services. All our practices are on the ground floor enabling wheel chair access and Shepherds Bush practice has a disabled toilet. We are entrusted by several Primary Care Trusts for providing the NHS Dental Emergency Service for North West London which operates 365 days a year. We also operate a Private Dental Emergency Service.
